cqs: How many relations are described between c1 and at least 999 things?
How many relations are proposed between c1 and at least 999 things?
How many things may c1 do with at least 999 things?
How many relations exist between c1 and at least 999 things?
How many things can c1 do with at least 999 things?
How many relations are there between c1 and at least 999 things?
How many relations are available between c1 and at least 999 things?
How many things could c1 do with at least 999 things?
query: SELECT (COUNT(?x) AS ?cnt) WHERE { <c1> rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty ?x ; owl:onClass [ owl:intersectionOf rdf:nil ] ; owl:minQualifiedCardinality "999"^^xsd:nonNegativeInteger ] . }
